This project is a game, in double meaning.

The development process itself is a game, and the purpose is to produce a game.
See Project rules.txt for more info about the process.

See license.txt for the license.

Building the project
You need to get
Allegro 4.9	http://sourceforge.net/projects/alleg/files/allegro-unstable/
Box2D		http://code.google.com/p/box2d/
sinxml		http://github.com/trezker/sinxml
premake4	http://industriousone.com/premake/download

Use premake4 to generate project files for your toolset
premake4 <toolset>
See http://industriousone.com/premake-quick-start

Then build the project using your toolset

You don't have to execute premake4 if you've only changed code within existing files.
